  "title": "Sales Associate/Executive (5D/Jurong East/Office System Furniture) - JT",
  "description": "<p><strong>$2500-2800 + commission + transport claimable</strong><br /><strong>Mon - Fri 9am - 6.30pm</strong><br /><strong>IMM Building </strong></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Attend to walk-in, online, and corporate enquiries to understand customer requirements and recommend suitable system furniture solutions.</li><li>Conduct onsite client meetings to assess space requirements, discuss layout concepts, and present furniture proposals.</li><li>Present product features, specifications, and space-planning solutions professionally to clients.</li><li>Prepare quotations, follow up on sales leads, and close sales transactions.</li><li>Coordinate with designers, project teams, and operations teams to ensure smooth project execution and timely delivery.</li><li>Maintain accurate sales records, customer databases, and sales documentation.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Prefer minimum 1 years of experience as sales associate.</li><li>Comfortable conducting onsite client meetings and site assessments.</li><li>Good communication, presentation, and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Customer-oriented mindset with strong sales drive.</li></ul><p>Company Name: Nala Employment Pte Ltd | License No.: 16C8302<br />EA Personnel Name: Tan Zhi Ning<br />EA Personnel No: R23116671</p>",
